Name: To the earth
About the game: Drive in the space! You are going to go to the earth from mars. drive safe! Gameplay This game does not have special goal but driving forward. Takes ~10 minutes each game Easy control(WASD or arrow keys) High-speed drifting (need unlock special car) Enjoy the music and the vibe. Features 5 cars and 2 types of cars. normal and drift. POV camera is ready 3 unique stages Story It is just the ordinary commute of a man living on mars. drive safe to your work!
